<seg id=1> South Korean army had continuous accidents, and the opposition party urged Defense Minister to resign. </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Reuters, Seoul The Korean opposition party asked South Korea's Defense Minister Kim Dong-Shin to resign because the army had been involved in many accidents, including launching military missiles and flares on civilians' residential areas. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> A South Korea official said that the latest story was that something was wrong with yesterday's military manoeuvre, and the bullets of flares broke through two walls of an old lady's house. </seg>
<seg id=4> The old lady's home was near the place where bits of missiles dropped after exposures two days ago. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=5> A navy official said that the ground troops of the South Korea Navy launched flares farther than expected, and landed on a civilian's house. </seg>
<seg id=6> Inchon is to the west of Seoul. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=7> A statement of Guomingdang said: "Defense Minister Kim Dong-Shin must resign, otherwise, (President Kim Dae Jung) must remove him from office. </seg>
<seg id=8> The government that is not afraid of the people is not the people's government." </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=9> The statement said: "Kim Dong-Shin tried to keep his position. He only expressed his apology... This is self-important." </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=10> The Ministry of Defense made apology for the missile accident yesterday. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=11> A navy official said that after the bullets of flares broke through two walls, they got into the bathroom. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=12> He said that the 83-year-old lady was frightened so much that she was sent to a hospital nearby. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=13> Last Friday, the South Korean army launched a ground-to-air missile and it exploded in the air by accident, and 3 civilians were wounded. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=14> An official of the Defense Ministry said that when the technicians of the air force base in Inchon, the Western harbor city, made a military inspection, they found the missile by accident. </seg>
<seg id=15> Inchon is 40gm away from the border of South Korea and North Korea. </seg>
</p>
